events.title: Monday Music Jam
events.description: Monday Music Jam is an open audience jam for people who want to try musical improv comedy.  We start each jam with a vocal warm up led by our pianist, then we break into groups and perform montage scene to song musical improv.  Participation is not mandatory and you can feel free to sit and watch.
